      <text><![CDATA[<p>Milwa sold goods worth {@total_sales@}. She got a commission of {@comm_amount@}. Calculate percentage commission.</p>
<p>Percentage commission = [[input:ans1]] [[validation:ans1]] [[feedback:prt1]]</p>]]></text>
